NEW DIRECTIONS IN COLLECTION DEVELOPMENT.

AFTER A BRIEF HISTORICAL BACKGROUND TO PRESENT PROBLEMS IN COLLECTION
DEVELOPMENT, INCLUDING THE RISING COST AND INCREASING IMPORTANCE OF SERIALS,
